<mvc:View controllerName="appartments.controller.View1" xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" displayBlock="true" xmlns="sap.m" xmlns:w="sap.ui.webc.main" xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout">
    <Page id="page" title="{i18n>title}">
        <!-- CreateDialog View is Loaded Below -->
        <mvc:XMLView id="_IDGenXMLView1" viewName="appartments.view.CreateDialog" />
        <!-- Table -->
        <ScrollContainer id="_IDGenScrollContainer1" horizontal="true">
            <Table id="idProducts" selectionChange="onRowSelection" width="120%" items="{/APPARTMENTSHeadersSet}" alternateRowColors="true" growing="false" growingScrollToLoad="false" mode="SingleSelectMaster">
                <columns>
                    <Column id="Id">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText1" text="Identifiant" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="Desc">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText2" text="Description" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="NbrPieces">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText3" text="Nbr.Pieces" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="NbrChambres">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText4" text="Nbr.Chambres" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="NbrSalleDeBains">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText5" text="Salles de descriptionain" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="Superficie">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText6" text="Superficie" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="Etage">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText7" text="Etage" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="Garage">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText8" text="Garage" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="Ascenseur">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText9" text="Ascenseur" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="Climatisation">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText10" text="Climatisation" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="PrixNuitee">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText11" text="Prix/Nuitee" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column id="Disponible">
                        <Text id="_IDGenText12" text="Disponible" />
                    </Column>
                </columns>
                <items>
                    <ColumnListItem id="_IDGenColumnListItem1" press=".onRowPress">
                        <cells>
                            <Text id="_IDGenText13" text="{Identifiant}" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <ExpandableText id="_IDGenExpandableText1" text="{Description}" maxCharacters="7" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <Text id="_IDGenText15" text="{NbrPieces}" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <Text id="_IDGenText16" text="{NbrChambres}" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <Text id="_IDGenText17" text="{NbrSalleDeBains}" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <Text id="_IDGenText18" text="{= parseInt(${Superficie})}" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <Text id="_IDGenText19" text="{Etage}" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <w:Badge id="_IDGenBadge1" colorScheme="{= ${Garage} === 'X' ? '6' : '1' }" text="{= ${Garage} === 'X' ? 'Avec' : 'Sans' }" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <w:Badge id="_IDGenBadge2" colorScheme="{= ${Ascenseur} === 'X' ? '6' : '1' }" text="{= ${Ascenseur} === 'X' ? 'Avec' : 'Sans' }" />
                            <!-- <Text id="_IDGenText21" text="{= ${Ascenseur} === 'X' ? 'Avec' : 'Sans' }"></Text> -->
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <w:Badge id="_IDGenBadge3" colorScheme="{= ${Climatisation} === 'X' ? '6' : '1' }" text="{= ${Climatisation} === 'X' ? 'Avec' : 'Sans' }" />
                            <!-- <Text id="_IDGenText22" text="{= ${Climatisation} === 'X' ? 'Avec' : 'Sans' }"></Text> -->
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <Text id="_IDGenText23" text="{= parseInt(${PrixNuitee})} MAD" />
                        </cells>
                        <cells>
                            <w:Badge id="_IDGenBadge4" colorScheme="{= ${Disponible} === 'X' ? '8' : '2' }" text="{= ${Disponible} === 'X' ? 'Disponible' : 'Indisponible' }" />
                            <!-- <Text id="_IDGenText24" text="{= ${Disponible} === 'X' ? 'Disponible' : 'Indisponible' }"></Text> -->
                        </cells>
                    </ColumnListItem>
                </items>
            </Table>
        </ScrollContainer>
    </Page>
</mvc:View>
